o-o-old</em>) weather gear from Castelli, Gore, Giordana, and Pearl Izumi, plus lights from Specialized, Garmin, and Niterider, Competitive Cyclist has what you need to spin through until spring!</p><p>Here are some of their top picks for men and women, from jackets to bibs, caps to gloves…</p><h2>Jackets</h2><p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite.jpg\" alt=\"Competitive Cyclist Jacket Composite\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/28120922/Competitive-Cyclist-Jacket-Composite-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></p><p>Your outer layer might just be the most important piece for keeping cold air, or rain or snow, at bay. Layer one of these jackets on top to keep yourself protected from the elements.</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fcastelli-alpha-ros-2-jacket-mens&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather|xid:fr1635872518862bde\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fcastelli-alpha-ros-2-jacket-mens&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather\" data-ml-id=\"0\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1635872518862bde\">Castelli Alpha RoS 2 Jacket – Men’s</a> — $370</li><li><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fcastelli-perfetto-ros-convertible-jacket-mens&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather|xid:fr1635872518862ibf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fcastelli-perfetto-ros-convertible-jacket-mens&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather\" data-ml-id=\"1\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1635872518862ibf\">Castelli Perfetto RoS Convertible Jacket – Men’s</a> — $270</li><li><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fgore-wear-c5-gore-tex-infinium-thermo-jacket-mens-gwrg02x&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather|xid:fr1635872518862hja\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competitivecyclist.com%2Fgore-wear-c5-gore-tex-infinium-thermo-jacket-mens-gwrg02x&amp;ctc=brspapparelbikingcccoldweather\" data-ml-id=\"2\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1635872518862hja\">Gore Wear C5 GORE-TEX Infinium Thermo Jacket – Men’s</a> — $220</li><li><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=92594cfb-2b30-40ba-ab76-f9c20ed4612c&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.competit